#: apps/api/serializers.py:1288 apps/core/forms.py:767
msgid "The transcription on which to perform alignment."
msgstr "进行对齐的转录。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1293 apps/core/forms.py:772
msgid "The reference text for alignment; must be a .txt file."
msgstr "对齐的参考文本；必须是.txt文件。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1298 apps/core/forms.py:777
msgid "Reuse a previously-uploaded reference text."
msgstr "重复使用先前的参考文本。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1301 apps/core/forms.py:780
msgid "N-gram"
msgstr "n-gram"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1306 apps/core/forms.py:785
msgid ""
"Length (2–25) of token sequences to compare; 25 should work well for at "
"least moderately clean OCR. For very poor OCR, lower to 3 or 4."
msgstr ""
"代币序列的长度(2-25)；25应至少适度清洁的OCR效果很好。对于非常差的OCR，较低至3"
"或4。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1309 apps/core/forms.py:788
msgid "Max offset"
msgstr "最大偏移"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1310 apps/core/forms.py:789
msgid ""
"Enables max-offset and disables beam search. Maximum number of characters "
"(20–80) difference between the aligned witness text and the original "
"transcription."
msgstr ""
"启用最大偏移并禁用束搜索。设置对齐的见证文本与原始转录之间允许的最大字符差"
"（20–80）。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1316 apps/core/forms.py:795
msgid "Beam size"
msgstr "束宽度"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1317 apps/core/forms.py:796
msgid ""
"Enables beam search; if this and max offset are left unset, beam search will "
"be on and beam size set to 20. Higher beam size (1-100) will result in "
"slower computation but more accurate results."
msgstr ""
"启用束搜索；如果将其和最大偏移保持不设定，则束搜索将打开，并且束尺寸设置为"
"20。较高的束尺寸(1-100)将导致计算较慢，但结果更准确。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1323 apps/core/forms.py:802
msgid "Gap"
msgstr "间隔"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1328 apps/core/forms.py:807
msgid ""
"The distance between matching unique n-grams; 600 should work well for clean "
"OCR or texts where passages align to different portions of the witness text. "
"To force end-to-end alignment of two documents, increase to 1,000,000."
msgstr ""
"匹配唯一的n-gram之间的距离；600应该适合清洁的OCR或文本与见证文本的不同部分保"
"持一致的文本。要强制两个文件的端到端对齐，请增加到1,000,000。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1331 apps/core/forms.py:810
msgid "Merge aligned text with existing transcription"
msgstr "合并对齐文本与现有转录"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1334 apps/core/forms.py:813
msgid ""
"If checked, the aligner will reuse the text of the original transcription "
"when alignment could not be performed; if unchecked, those lines will be "
"blank."
msgstr ""
"如果选中了，当无法执行对齐时，对准器将重复使用原始转录的文本；如果未选中，这"
"些行将为空白。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1337 apps/core/forms.py:816
msgid "Use full transcribed document"
msgstr "使用完整转录的文档"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1340 apps/core/forms.py:819
msgid ""
"If checked, the aligner will use all transcribed pages of the document to "
"find matches. If unchecked, it will compare each page to the text separately."
msgstr ""
"如果已检查，对准器将使用文档的所有转录页面查找匹配项。如果未选中，它将分别将"
"每个页面与文本进行比较。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1343 apps/core/forms.py:822
msgid "Line length match threshold"
msgstr "文本行长匹配阈值"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1344 apps/core/forms.py:823
msgid ""
"Minimum proportion (0.0–1.0) of aligned line length to original "
"transcription, below which matches are ignored. At 0.0, all matches are "
"accepted."
msgstr ""
"对齐文本行长度与原始转录的最小比例(0.0-1.0)，下面忽略了匹配。在0.0时，所有匹"
"配都被接受。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1353 apps/core/forms.py:833 apps/core/forms.py:854
msgid "Region types to include in the alignment."
msgstr "在对齐中包括的区域类型。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1357 apps/core/forms.py:837
msgid "Layer name"
msgstr "图层名称"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1358 apps/core/forms.py:838
msgid ""
"Name for the new transcription layer produced by this alignment. If you "
"reuse an existing layer name, the layer will be overwritten; use caution."
msgstr ""
"该对齐产生的新转录层的名称。如果您重复使用现有层名称，则该图层将被覆盖；谨慎"
"行事。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1379 apps/core/forms.py:865
msgid "You must supply a textual witness (reference text)."
msgstr "您必须提供文字见证(参考文本)。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1383 apps/core/forms.py:869
msgid "You may only supply one witness text (file upload or existing text)."
msgstr "您只能提供一个见证文本(文件上传或现有文本)。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1388 apps/core/forms.py:877
msgid ""
"Alignment layer name cannot be the same as the transcription you are trying "
"to align."
msgstr "对齐层名称不能与您要对齐的转录相同。"

#: apps/api/serializers.py:1395 apps/core/forms.py:884
msgid "Max offset and beam size cannot both be non-zero."
msgstr "最大偏移量和束尺寸不能均不为零。"

