#: escriptorium/templates/includes/help/baseline_editor.html:2
msgid ""
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"    <b>Left click</b> on the image to <u>create</u> new line, <b>Right "
"click</b> to <b>add points</b> and <b>Left click</b> again to <u>finish</u> "
"it.\n"
"    <br/>You can keep the mouse button pressed for free drawing.\n"
"    <br/>Hitting <b>escape</b> while drawing a line <u>cancels</u> it.\n"
"    <br/>If regions matter to you switch to region mode first <i class=\"fas "
"fa-th-large\"></i> (R key).\n"
"    <br/>when in region mode <b>Left click</b> to create a new rectangular "
"region, left click again to finish it.\n"
"    <br/>lines drawn inside a region will automatically be bound to it.\n"
"    <br/>When the quality of the segmentation is good, you can prompt the "
"system to calculate masks <i class=\"text-success fas fa-thumbs-up\"></i>,\n"
"    <br/>once a page already has masks new lines will automatically get a "
"mask and updating a line will also recalculate its mask.\n"
"    <br/><b>Note</b> that the quality of the masks is highly dependent on "
"the quality of the whole segmentation, not only the corresponding line,\n"
"    <br/>so make sure to draw all the lines before calculating the masks.\n"
"    <br>You can also have the option to calculate the masks <i>en masse</i> "
"in the Images tab -> segment -> choose 'Only masks'.\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"    <b>Left click</b> on a line to select it, then you can drag its closest "
"control point.\n"
"    <br/><b>Double click</b> on the line will create a <u>new control point</"
"u> at the mouse location.\n"
"    <br/>You can reverse the order of the line's points by selecting a line "
"(or multiple) and using reverse <i class=\"fas fa-arrow-alt-h\"></i> (I "
"key).\n"
"    <br/>When in region mode, Regions can be edited the same way.\n"
"    <br/>Selected lines can be linked or unlinked to regions with the "
"corresponding buttons <i class=\"fas fa-link\"></i>(Y key) <i class=\"fas fa-"
"unlink\"> (U key).</i>\n"
"    <br/>By using the cut mode <i class=\"text-warning fas fa-cut\"></i> (C "
"key) you can cut through lines, splitting them in two or removing part of "
"them.\n"
"    <br/>If at least two lines are selected an option to join them becomes "
"available <i class=\"fas fa-compress-arrows-alt\"></i> (J key).\n"
"    <br/>You can go through your changes <u>history</u> back and forth with "
"<b>Ctrl+Z</b>(undo) and <b>Ctrl+Y</b>(redo) or by using the corresponding "
"buttons <i class=\"fas fa-undo\"></i><i class=\"fas fa-redo\"></i>.\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"    <b>Shift+click</b> allows to add or remove a line from the <u>selection</"
"u>,\n"
"    <br/>Clicking on an empty space clears the selection,\n"
"    <br/><b>shift and drag</b> creates a <u>lasso</u> selection tool that "
"allows to select control points (they then appear black).\n"
"    <br/><b>Note:</b> If lines are already selected the lasso will only "
"select points in those lines.\n"
"    <br/><b>Ctrl+drag</b> allows to move all the selected control points at "
"once (or the selected lines if no control points are selected).\n"
"\n"
"    <br/>The red trash <i class=\"text-danger fas fa-trash\"></i> button "
"<b>deletes</b> all selected <b>lines/regions</b>,\n"
"    <br/>The yellow trash button <i class=\"text-warning fas fa-trash\"></i> "
"only <b>deletes</b> selected control <b>points</b>.\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"<b>图像上的左键单击</b> <u>创建新行，<b>右键单击</b> <b> <b>添加点</b> and "
"<b> <b> <b>再次单击</b>再次单击</b>到<u> teright </u> it </u> IT。\n"
"<br/>您可以按下鼠标按钮免费绘图。\n"
"<br/>敲击<b>逃脱</b>绘制线路<u>取消</u> it。\n"
"<br/>如果区域与您至关重要，请切换到区域模式，首先<i class =“ fas fa-thlage”> "
"</i>(r键)。\n"
"<br/>在区域模式下<b>左键单击</b>以创建一个新的矩形区域，请再次单击以完成"
"它。\n"
"<br/>在区域内绘制的线将自动与之绑定。\n"
"<br/>当分割的质量良好时，您可以提示系统计算掩码<i class =“ text-success fas "
"fa-thumbs-up”> </i>,\n"
"<br/>一页已经有一个掩码后，新行将自动获取掩码，并且更新线路还将重新计算其面"
"罩。\n"
"<br/> <b> note </b> </b>掩码的质量高度取决于整个分割的质量，不仅是相应的"
"行，\n"
"<br/>因此，请确保在计算口罩之前绘制所有线条。\n"
"<br>您还可以选择在“图像”选项卡 - > segment->中计算蒙版<i> en Masse </i>  - >"
"选择“仅蒙版”。\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"<b>左键单击</b>在一条线上选择它，然后可以拖动其最接近的控制点。\n"
"<br/> <b>双点击</b>在行上将在鼠标位置创建一个新的控制点</u>。\n"
"<br/>您可以通过选择一条线(或多个)并使用反向<i class =“ fas fa-arrow-alt-h”> "
"</i>(i键)来逆转行点的顺序。\n"
"<br/>在区域模式下，可以以相同的方式编辑区域。\n"
"<br/>选定的行可以通过相应的按钮<i class =“ fas fa-link”> </i>(y键)<i class "
"=“ fas fa-unlink”>(u键)。\n"
"<br/>通过使用剪切模式<i class =“文本绘制fas fa-cut”> </i>(c键)，您可以切开"
"线，将它们分成两个或删除部分。\n"
"<br/>如果选择了至少两行以加入它们的选项，则可以使用<i class =“ fas fa-"
"compress-arrows-alt”> </i>(j键)。\n"
"<br/>您可以使用<b> ctrl+z </b>(undo)和<b> ctrl+y </b>(redo)或使用相应的按钮"
"<i class =“ fa-undo”> fa-undo“> </i> class =” fa-fa-redo fa-redo </> </> </> "
"</> </> </> <\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"<b> shift+单击</b>允许从<u>选择</u>中添加或删除一行\n"
"<br/>单击空白空间可以清除选择，\n"
"<br/> <b> shift and drag </b>创建<u> lasso </u>选择工具，可以选择控制点(然后"
"它们出现黑色)。\n"
"<br/> <b>注意: </b>如果已经选择了行，则套索仅在这些行中选择点。\n"
"<br/> <b> ctrl+drag </b>允许一次移动所有选定的控制点(或者如果未选择控制点，则"
"选择的行)。\n"
"\n"
"<br/>红色垃圾<i class =“ text-danger fas fa-trash”> </i> button <b> deletes "
"</b>所有选定的<b> lines/regions </b>,\n"
"<br/>黄色垃圾按钮<i class =“文本绘制FA-FA-TRASH”> </i>仅<b> deletes </b>选定"
"的控件<b>点</b>。\n"
"</p>\n"

#: escriptorium/templates/includes/help/compare_transcriptions.html:2
msgid ""
"\n"
"<p style=\"direction:ltr\">\n"
"    Each line is a different transcription as checked in the transcription "
"management window <i class=\"fas fa-cog\"></i>\n"
"    <br>The colors represent the difference with the current transcription,\n"
"    <br><font color=\"green\">green</font> characters are not present in the "
"current (editable) transcription while <font color=\"red\">red</font> "
"characters are not present in the compared transcription.\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<p style =“方向: ltr”>\n"
"每行都是不同的转录，如在“转录管理”窗口中检查的，<i class =“ fas fa-cog”> </"
"i>\n"
"<br>颜色代表与当前转录的差异，\n"
"<br> <font color =“绿色”>绿色</font>字符在当前(可编辑)转录中不存在，而<font "
"color =“ red”> red </font> red </font>在比较的转录中不存在。\n"
"</p>\n"

#: escriptorium/templates/includes/help/versions.html:2
msgid ""
"\n"
"<p style=\"direction:ltr\">\n"
"    Each line corresponds to an edition of the content, in inverse "
"chronological order (Most recent at the top).\n"
"    <br>The colors represent the difference with the previous version,\n"
"    <br><font color=\"green\">green</font> are <b>additions</b> while <font "
"color=\"red\">red</font> are <b>deletions</b>,\n"
"    <br>meaning red characters are not actually part of the line anymore, "
"they are displayed to easily spot the differences.\n"
"    <br>You can mouse over the text to see the actual content.\n"
"    <br>The load state button <i class=\"fas fa-file-upload\"></i> simply "
"revert the content of the line to the corresponding text version.\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<p style =“方向: ltr”>\n"
"每行以反时间顺序(最新的最新时间)对应于内容的版本。\n"
"<br>颜色代表了上一个版本的区别，\n"
"<br> <font color =“绿色”>绿色</font>是<b>加法</b>而<font color =“ red”> red "
"</font>是<b>删除</b>,\n"
"<br>意味着红色字符实际上不再是该行的一部分，而是显示它们以轻松发现差异。\n"
"<br>您可以在文本上鼠标以查看实际内容。\n"
"<br> load状态按钮<i class =“ FA FA FA-FILE-UPLOAD”> </i>只需将行的内容还原为"
"相应的文本版本即可。\n"
"</p>\n"

